
'''Athmane Ariouet''' yavutse ku ya 24 Nzeri 1948 ni umukinnyi wa sinema, ikinamico na filimi zica kuri televiziyo muri [[Aligeriya|Alijeriya]]<ref>https://www.liberte-algerie.com/culture/athmane-ariouet-le-banni-decore-342517</ref>. Ariouet ufatwa nk'umwe mu bakinnyi beza kandi bazwi cyane muri sinema yo muri [[Aligeriya|Alijeriya]], yahawe ibihembo byinshi mu mwuga umaze imyaka irenga mirongo itanu.<ref>https://www.echoroukonline.com/le-geant-du-cinema-athmane-ariouet-sadresse-aux-algeriens</ref> 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Ariouet yavutse ku ya 24 Nzeri 1948 i Amdoukal muri Barika, muri wilaya ya Batna. Yabanje kwitabira konserwatori ya Algiers kuva 1969 kugeza 1972<ref>https://www.dzairdaily.com/algerie-acteur-athmane-ariouet-fait-grand-retour-instagram/</ref>.

== Umwuga ==
Mugihe cyishuri, yari afite ishyaka ryo kuba umukinnyi wa filimi mwiza.  Yemeje bose gutsindira igihembo cya mbere kubera inkoranyamagambo yakoze mu [[gifaransa]]<ref>https://izzoran.com/biographies-personnalites-algeriennes/cinema-biographies-personnalites-algeriennes/athmane-ariouet/</ref>. Yatinze, kuba umwizerwa mu gukina yatewe inkunga n’umwarimu w’igifaransa Henri Vangret<ref>https://www.algerieinfos.com/apres-20-ans-de-censure-le-dernier-film-dathmane-ariouet-bientot-sur-les-ecrans/</ref>. Nyuma yize ikinamico yicyarabu hamwe nabakinnyi bakomeye Mustapha Kasdarli, Taha Laâmiri na Allal Mouhib<ref>https://artsandculture.google.com/entity/g11b6d6k_r6?hl=de</ref>. Umukino we wa mbere wa sinema yakinnye muri 1963 ''Le Résultat'' . Mu 1981, yakinnye muri filime ya televiziyo ''The Executioner Cries'' iyobowe na Abder Isker.<ref>https://www.inter-lignes.com/reapparition-rejouissante-dathmane-ariouet/</ref> 

Filime ye yo mu bwoko bwa ''Carnaval Fi Dechra yo mu'' 1994, ifatwa nka filimi idahwema kwishyiriraho politiki. Iyi filime yayobowe na Mohamed Oukassi, ni filime isetsa yerekana umuryango wa [[Alijeriya]] usebanya. Icyakora, yabujijwe gukina nyuma ya filime<ref>https://www.cineserie.com/persons/3042531/</ref>. Mu 2002, yagarutse muri sinema akina na filime ''El Arch'' iyobowe na perezida. Ukuboza 2003, yasohoye filime ye ya mbere ''Er-roubla'' yakoranye na ENTV<ref>https://www.elkhadra.com/fr/sequences-darchives-athmane-ariouet/</ref>.  

Mu 2004, yasezeye mu gukina nyuma ya filime ''Chronique des années pub'' aho yahuye n’ibibazo by’amafaranga ndetse no guhagarika ikinamico. Icyakora, mu 2017 mu ihuriro rya buri munsi rya El Moudjahid, uwahoze ari Minisitiri w’umuco Azzedine Mihoubi yavuze ko “iyi filime yari mu cyiciro cyo gutunganya” kandi amaherezo yasohotse mu 2018<ref>https://www.vinyculture.com/athmane-ariouet-recoit-la-medaille-achir/</ref>. Muri Nyakanga 2020, Ariouet yahawe imidari ya “Achir” yashyizwe ku rwego rw'igihugu iyobowe na Perezida wa Repubulika Abdelmadjid Tebboune <ref>https://steamcommunity.com/id/athmaneariouet</ref>. 

